      "code": "<?php\n// Delete default Hello World post\n$hello_world = get_posts(array('title' => 'Hello world!', 'post_type' => 'post'));\nif (!empty($hello_world)) {\n    wp_delete_post($hello_world[0]->ID, true);\n}\n\n// Create the open letter post\n$post_id = wp_insert_post(array(\n    'post_title' => 'An Open Letter to Matt Mullenweg',\n    'post_content' => '<!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"is-style-alert\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-style-alert\">\\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":1,\"fontSize\":\"huge\"} -->\\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-huge-font-size\">AN OPEN LETTER</h1>\\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":2,\"fontSize\":\"large\"} -->\\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-large-font-size\">TO MATT MULLENWEG</h2>\\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\\n</div>\\n<!-- /wp:group -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"is-style-highlight\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-style-highlight\">\\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>September 17, 2025</strong></p>\\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\\n</div>\\n<!-- /wp:group -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:group {\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\">\\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"large\"} -->\\n<p class=\"has-large-font-size\"><strong>Hi Matt,</strong></p>\\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>I will get straight to it. I have been building with WordPress for many years and I am passionate about creating fast, thoughtful block themes that help people share ideas and tell stories. I created the site you are on now last night using the block editor especially for this letter.</p>\\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Lately I have applied to several openings at Automattic and each time I receive a same day rejection email with no opportunity for a chat or interview. The most recent role I applied for was a position focused on quickly producing block theme websites for customers, which is exactly the kind of work I want to do.</p>\\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>I respect that hiring at scale is difficult and that many strong candidates apply. I am writing because Automattic is where I want to be and I would welcome even a short conversation to show my work, hear feedback, and explore whether there might be a fit. If there is someone on your team who reviews these roles and portfolios, I would be grateful for a pointer.</p>\\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Thank you for creating and guiding an ecosystem that keeps WordPress alive and useful for so many people. I appreciate your time and any advice you can offer.</p>\\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\\n</div>\\n<!-- /wp:group -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"is-style-success\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-style-success\">\\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"large\"} -->\\n<p class=\"has-large-font-size\"><strong>Warmly,</strong></p>\\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"large\"} -->\\n<p class=\"has-large-font-size\"><strong>Billy Wilcosky</strong></p>\\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p><a href=\"https://wilcosky.com\" target=\"_blank\">wilcosky.com</a></p>\\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\\n</div>\\n<!-- /wp:group -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide\"/>\\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"is-style-highlight\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-style-highlight\">\\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":2,\"fontSize\":\"large\"} -->\\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-large-font-size\">ABOUT THIS DEMO</h2>\\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">This website demonstrates the <strong>New Kid</strong> NeoBrutalism WordPress block theme, built specifically to showcase modern block theme development skills. Everything was created using WordPress native block editor.</p>\\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\\n<!-- wp:buttons {\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\",\"justifyContent\":\"center\"}} -->\\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons\">\\n<!-- wp:button {\"className\":\"is-style-alert\"} -->\\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-alert\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https://github.com/zerosonesfun/new-kid\" target=\"_blank\">VIEW THEME ON GITHUB</a></div>\\n<!-- /wp:button -->\\n</div>\\n<!-- /wp:buttons -->\\n</div>\\n<!-- /wp:group -->',\n    'post_status' => 'publish',\n    'post_type' => 'post',\n    'post_category' => array(1)\n));\n?>"
